This program should be run on MacOS with make -f Makefile.mac run
One window opens,named "Assignment 4".
A colored cube is shown allowing the following usage:

Usage: Right Click main window named Assignment 4 and choose to select current transformation to be applied (scale, rotate or translate)
Press: 1 - to increase transform in X axis
Press: 2 - to decrease transform in X axis
Press: 3 - to increase transform in Y axis
Press: 4 - to decrease transform in Y axis
Press: 5 - to increase transform in Z axis
Press: 6 - to decrease transform in Z axis
Press: 7 - to increase delta for current transform
Press: 8 - to decrease delta for current transform
Press: r - to reset all transformations and deltas to default
Press: q - to quit

